# redis
1. `sudo apt install redis-server`
2. redis-server --version
   1. Redis server v=5.0.7 malloc=jemalloc-5.2.1
3. service redis-server start


# sqlight
1. `apt install sqlite3`
2. sqlite3 --version
   1. 3.31.1 2020-01-27
